<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="lo">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <meta name="description" content="ແກ້ໄຂລົດມືສອງ">
    <title>ແກ້ໄຂລົດ</title>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Noto+Sans+Lao:wght@400;600&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/style.css">
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
</head>
<body>
    <nav class="navbar navbar-expand-lg navbar-dark bg-dark">
        <div class="container">
            <a class="navbar-brand" href="/admin/dashboard">
                <img src="/images/logo.png" alt="Logo" style="height: 80px; margin-right: 15px;">
                ແຜງຄວບຄຸມແອດມິນ
            </a>
            <button class="navbar-toggler" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#navbarNav" aria-controls="navbarNav" aria-expanded="false" aria-label="Toggle navigation">
                <span class="navbar-toggler-icon"></span>
            </button>
            <div class="collapse navbar-collapse" id="navbarNav">
                <div class="navbar-nav ms-auto">
                    <a class="nav-link" href="/admin/manage-car">ຈັດການລົດ</a>
                    <a class="nav-link" href="/admin/add-car">ເພີ່ມລົດໃໝ່</a>
                    <a class="nav-link" href="/admin/manage-sell-requests">ຈັດການຄຳຂໍຂາຍ</a>
                    <a class="nav-link" href="/">ໜ້າຫຼັກ</a>
                    <a class="nav-link text-danger" href="/admin/logout" onclick="return confirm('ທ່ານແນ່ໃຈບໍ່ທີ່ຈະອອກຈາກລະບົບ?');">ອອກຈາກລະບົບ</a>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </nav>

    <div class="container mt-4">
        <div class="card bg-dark text-light">
            <div class="card-header bg-gold text-dark">
                <h2>ແກ້ໄຂລົດ</h2>
            </div>
            <div class="card-body">
                <% if (error) { %>
                    <div class="alert alert-danger alert-dismissible fade show" role="alert">
                        <%- error %>
                        <button type="button" class="btn-close" data-bs-dismiss="alert" aria-label="Close"></button>
                    </div>
                <% } %>
                <form action="/admin/edit-car/<%- car._id %>" method="post" enctype="multipart/form-data">
                    <input type="hidden" name="existingImages" value="<%- JSON.stringify(car.images) %>">
                    <div class="mb-3">
                        <label class="form-label">ຍີ່ຫໍ້</label>
                        <select name="brand" class="form-control" required>
                            <option value="Toyota" <%- car.brand === 'Toyota' ? 'selected' : '' %>>Toyota</option>
                            <option value="Honda" <%- car.brand === 'Honda' ? 'selected' : '' %>>Honda</option>
                            <option value="Mazda" <%- car.brand === 'Mazda' ? 'selected' : '' %>>Mazda</option>
                            <option value="Mitsubishi" <%- car.brand === 'Mitsubishi' ? 'selected' : '' %>>Mitsubishi</option>
                            <option value="Isuzu" <%- car.brand === 'Isuzu' ? 'selected' : '' %>>Isuzu</option>
                            <option value="Nissan" <%- car.brand === 'Nissan' ? 'selected' : '' %>>Nissan</option>
                        </select>
                    </div>
                    <div class="mb-3">
                        <label class="form-label">ລຸ້ນ</label>
                        <input type="text" name="model" class="form-control" value="<%- car.model %>" required>
                    </div>
                    <div class="mb-3">
                        <label class="form-label">ປະເພດລົດ</label>
                        <select name="carType" class="form-control" required>
                            <option value="Sedan" <%- car.carType === 'Sedan' ? 'selected' : '' %>>ລົດເກົງ (Sedan)</option>
                            <option value="Hatchback" <%- car.carType === 'Hatchback' ? 'selected' : '' %>>ລົດແຮທຊ໌ແບັກ (Hatchback)</option>
                            <option value="Pickup" <%- car.carType === 'Pickup' ? 'selected' : '' %>>ລົດກະບະ (Pickup)</option>
                            <option value="Crossover" <%- car.carType === 'Crossover' ? 'selected' : '' %>>ລົດຄຣອສໂອເວີ (Crossover)</option>
                            <option value="SUV" <%- car.carType === 'SUV' ? 'selected' : '' %>>ລົດ SUV</option>
                            <option value="PPV" <%- car.carType === 'PPV' ? 'selected' : '' %>>ລົດ PPV</option>
                            <option value="MPV" <%- car.carType === 'MPV' ? 'selected' : '' %>>ລົດ MPV</option>
                        </select>
                    </div>
                    <div class="mb-3">
                        <label class="form-label">ປີ</label>
                        <input type="number" name="year" class="form-control" value="<%- car.year %>" required min="1900" max="<%- new Date().getFullYear() %>">
                    </div>
                    <div class="mb-3">
                        <label class="form-label">ລາຄາ</label>
                        <input type="number" name="price" class="form-control" value="<%- car.price %>" required min="0">
                    </div>
                    <div class="mb-3">
                        <label class="form-label">ເກຍ</label>
                        <select name="transmission" class="form-control" required>
                            <option value="Automatic" <%- car.transmission === 'Automatic' ? 'selected' : '' %>>ອັດຕະໂນມັດ</option>
                            <option value="Manual" <%- car.transmission === 'Manual' ? 'selected' : '' %>>ຄູ່ມື</option>
                        </select>
                    </div>
                    <div class="mb-3">
                        <label class="form-label">ໄມລ໌</label>
                        <input type="number" name="mileage" class="form-control" value="<%- car.mileage || '' %>" placeholder="ກິໂລແມັດ" min="0">
                    </div>
                    <div class="mb-3">
                        <label class="form-label">ລາຍລະອຽດ</label>
                        <textarea name="description" class="form-control" rows="4" placeholder="ລາຍລະອຽດລົດ"><%- car.description || '' %></textarea>
                    </div>
                    <div class="mb-3">
                        <label class="form-label">ແຂວງ</label>
                        <select name="province" class="form-control" required>
                            <option value="">ເລືອກແຂວງ</option>
                            <% provinces.forEach(province => { %>
                                <option value="<%- province %>" <%- car.province === province ? 'selected' : '' %>><%- province %></option>
                            <% }) %>
                        </select>
                    </div>
                    <div class="mb-3">
                        <label class="form-label">ຮູບພາບປັດຈຸບັນ</label>
                        <div class="row">
                            <% car.images.forEach((image, index) => { %>
                                <div class="col-md-3 mb-2">
                                    <img src="<%- image %>" class="img-thumbnail" alt="Image <%- index %>">
                                </div>
                            <% }) %>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="mb-3">
                        <label class="form-label">ເພີ່ມຮູບພາບໃໝ່ (ສູງສຸດ 10 ຮູບ)</label>
                        <input type="file" name="images" class="form-control" multiple accept="image/*">
                    </div>
                    <div class="mb-3">
                        <label class="form-label">ເລືອກຮູບປົກ</label>
                        <input type="number" name="coverImageIndex" class="form-control" value="<%- car.images.indexOf(car.coverImage) >= 0 ? car.images.indexOf(car.coverImage) : 0 %>" min="0" max="9" placeholder="ດັດສະນີຮູບ (0-9)">
                    </div>
                    <div class="mb-3">
                        <label class="form-label">ສະຖານະການກວດສອບ</label>
                        <div class="form-check">
                            <input class="form-check-input" type="checkbox" name="noFlood" id="noFlood" <%- car.inspected.noFlood ? 'checked' : '' %>>
                            <label class="form-check-label" for="noFlood">ບໍ່ເຄີຍຖືກນໍ້າຖ້ວມ</label>
                        </div>
                        <div class="form-check">
                            <input class="form-check-input" type="checkbox" name="noMajorAccident" id="noMajorAccident" <%- car.inspected.noMajorAccident ? 'checked' : '' %>>
                            <label class="form-check-label" for="noMajorAccident">ບໍ່ເຄີຍປະສົບອຸປະຕິເຫດໜັກ</label>
                        </div>
                        <div class="form-check">
                            <input class="form-check-input" type="checkbox" name="noFire" id="noFire" <%- car.inspected.noFire ? 'checked' : '' %>>
                            <label class="form-check-label" for="noFire">ບໍ່ເຄີຍໄຟໄໝ້</label>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="mb-3">
                        <div class="form-check">
                            <input class="form-check-input" type="checkbox" name="isPremium" id="isPremium" <%- car.isPremium ? 'checked' : '' %>>
                            <label class="form-check-label" for="isPremium">ພຣີມຽມ</label>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="mb-3 d-flex gap-3">
                        <button type="submit" class="btn btn-gold">ບັນທຶກ</button>
                        <a href="/admin/manage-car" class="btn btn-outline-gold">ກັບຄືນ</a>
                    </div>
                </form>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <footer class="footer text-center bg-dark text-gold">
        <div class="container">
            <p>ທີ່ຢູ່: ນະຄອນຫຼວງວຽງຈັນ, ປະເທດລາວ</p>
            <p>ໂທ: +856 20 1234 5678</p>
            <p>ອີເມວ: contact@yourcarwebsite.com</p>
            <p>ຕິດຕາມພວກເຮົາ:
                <a href="https://www.facebook.com/yourpage" target="_blank" class="text-gold mx-2">Facebook</a> |
                <a href="https://www.tiktok.com/@your.tiktok" target="_blank" class="text-gold mx-2">TikTok</a>
            </p>
            <p>ດາວໂຫຼດແອັບ:
                <a href="https://play.google.com/store" target="_blank" class="text-gold mx-2">Google Play</a> |
                <a href="https://www.apple.com/app-store/" target="_blank" class="text-gold mx-2">App Store</a>
            </p>
            <p>© 2025 Used Car Sales. ສະຫງວນລິຂະສິດ.</p>
        </div>
    </footer>

    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js"></script>
</body>
</html>